{"id": 57724, "date": "2025-07-16T04:00:14", "date_gmt": "2025-07-16T11:00:14", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57724"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T10:30:06", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T17:30:06", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-16-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/16/kingdom-of-days-july-16-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 16"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays their second of six consecutive nights at the Pandemonium in Wanamassa, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce reschedules a planned gig at The Stone Balloon in Newark, Delaware for the following month.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band complete the recording of &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; at the Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to the New Orleans Municipal Auditorium, where the setlist features Bruce&#8217;s one and only cover of &#8220;Honky Tonk.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-xE7qS26M-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/xE7qS26M?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kJCwCcvLG9g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>At The Power Station in New York City, Bruce records &#8220;Ricky Wants a Man of Her Own&#8221; and &#8220;Cindy.&#8221; The former won&#8217;t be released for almost twenty years, the latter not for another fifteen years after that.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xuA_Q9iVyOY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZlI-L52KrnY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s five-night River stand at The Spectrum in Philly continues.</p>\n<div id=\"v-8V1HMlo9-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/8V1HMlo9?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28385\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-07-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?fit=1191%2C1080&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1191,1080\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-16\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?fit=300%2C272&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?fit=758%2C688&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28385 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?resize=758%2C687&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"687\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?w=1191&amp;ssl=1 1191w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?resize=300%2C272&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?resize=1024%2C929&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-16.jpg?resize=768%2C696&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1983:\u00a0</strong>Bruce guest-stars with Midnight Thunder for six songs at The Headliner in Neptune, New Jersey, including &#8220;Lucille,&#8221; &#8220;Wooly Bully,&#8221; and &#8220;Keep-a-Knockin&#8217;.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-rSVwCU6r-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/rSVwCU6r?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984: </strong>On a night off in between Born in the U.S.A. shows in Chicago, Bruce is spotted playing pinball at a local bar.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19635\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?fit=850%2C252&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"850,252\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-16\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?fit=300%2C89&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?fit=758%2C225&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19635 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?resize=758%2C225&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?w=850&amp;ssl=1 850w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?resize=300%2C89&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1984-07-16.png?resize=768%2C228&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>Bruce (along with Jon Bon Jovi, Patti, and Max) celebrates the 20th anniversary of The Stone Pony by joining Southside Johnny on stage for seven songs, including &#8220;I Played the Fool,&#8221; &#8220;Funky Broadway,&#8221; and &#8220;Jersey Girl.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytSVHBMmYqg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19547\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1994-07-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1994-07-16.jpg?fit=880%2C962&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"880,962\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&qu