escription=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1994-0716.jpg?fit=300%2C245&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1994-0716.jpg?fit=584%2C476&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3105 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1994-0716.jpg?resize=584%2C476&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"584\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1994-0716.jpg?w=584&amp;ssl=1 584w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1994-0716.jpg?resize=300%2C245&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1998: </strong>At a Sony trade show in Miami, Bruce announces an upcoming box set of unreleased tracks.</p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse for the upcoming Rising Tour.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11313\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/rehearsal-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"426,287\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"rehearsal\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?fit=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?fit=426%2C287&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11313 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?resize=426%2C287&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"426\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?w=426&amp;ssl=1 426w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/rehearsal.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>The Devils &amp; Dust Tour returns to the U.S., and the first show of the leg is at the Pepsi Arena in Albany. Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Does This Bus Stop at 82nd Street&#8221; for the occasion.</p>\n<div id=\"v-bYjdK3w0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/bYjdK3w0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28387\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2005-07-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?fit=2190%2C2264&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2190,2264\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2005-07-16\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?fit=290%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?fit=758%2C783&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28387 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=758%2C784&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"784\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?w=2190&amp;ssl=1 2190w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=290%2C300&amp;ssl=1 290w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=991%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 991w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=768%2C794&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=1486%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1486w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2005-07-16.jpg?resize=1981%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1981w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band bring the Working on a Dream Tour to Carhaix, France. The show is partially broadcast on French radio&#8211;listen to excerpts below:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/D-vlEKWeNNs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-sam